oacConfigMgmtMIBModule.name: oacConfigMgmtMIBModule

revisions.description: Added MODULE-COMPLIANCE AND OBJECT GROUP, fixed some minor corrections.
This MIB module describes a MIB for keeping track of changes on equipment's configuration.
